"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月9日，据官方消息，[EOS](https://www.bitcoin86.com/szb/eos/)生态DeFi平台Pizza在昨日遭黑客攻击，黑客账户itsspiderman利用溢出漏洞在eCurve凭空增发tripool做市凭证，在Pizza质押并借出协议中的绝大部分Token。Pizza平台在本次攻击中损失约500万美元。目前，Pizza正与慢雾科技、EOS节点、及广大目方合作尝试追回丢失资产。\",\"timestamp\":1639127389,\"title\":\"EOS生态DeFi平台Pizza遭攻击，损失约500万美元\"},\"digest\":\"0HbIYe9lAxdb9ukA6CkyLnDiHnPWS4TbvK01wTOCM-s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x95F496913837294B5aB92Fe5EA8a3b70B6c9310B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rpiwMU8_vocRfX1UlbXFnBktBe7y2sES3hQmI2knPIo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MvF4HUNlDgbjLgXYhlI7Hozfsefa5lbxoaORuL2FCEA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"OBQHC9B8Xdekk2-i7iPfiZ5KVymMhYdWFuOde-uw0qrtBSCjbq-0G75OX-wNrQ-4k_p7JhzhkoHUKfTqWdKejw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xea5cb6225b6d72e35ee7d99e45f3389b05721ffcd33e2b897b8b9e6df179fdef7ee6d670a4ab57211711a0520b1c0511ab421ad72d8778f4a9f3c644f0a660c21c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rpiwMU8_vocRfX1UlbXFnBktBe7y2sES3hQmI2knPIo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"MvF4HUNlDgbjLgXYhlI7Hozfsefa5lbxoaORuL2FCEA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"0HbIYe9lAxdb9ukA6CkyLnDiHnPWS4TbvK01wTOCM-s\"}"